precis:
Authority for STATISTICS CANADA to enter into an AGREEMENT with the
MANITOBA BUREAU OF STATISTICS which provides for the exchange of
statistical information based on surveys of federal and provincial
government enterprises and the provision of tabulations and analysis
based thereon.
